    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are nearly ready, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced halloumi</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until the halloumi is browned</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Ordered extra halloumi? Slice and cook in a pan with a little oil for 4-6 min or until golden all over</span></strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p>",
