    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, top your <strong>toasted ciabatta base</strong> with a <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>lettuce</strong> <strong>leaf</strong>, the<strong> chimichurri courgette</strong>,<strong> </strong>the <strong>browned halloumi </strong>and the <strong>toasted ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>chimichurri courgette & halloumi sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>lettuce</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> to the side with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and the<strong> remaining red wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>smokey potatoes & courgette </strong>to the side, then drizzle over the <strong>garlic sauce </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
